OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with a few spots
OL,6,Fof light rain, but some drier,
OL,7,Fbrighter spells developing for a time.
OL,8,FShowery outbreaks of rain will then
OL,9,Fdevelop through the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,12,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,13,FConditions will be rather murky for
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway, with occasional
OL,15,Fmist and fog patches.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with patchy
OL,18,Frain, clearing through the morning.
OL,19,FTurning brighter during the afternoon
OL,20,Fwith sunny spells developing and a few
OL,21,Fscattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
